    - All 15 TRNTYPE values (CREDIT, DEBIT, INT, DIV, FEE, SRVCHG, DEP, ATM, POS,
      XFER, CHECK, PAYMENT, CASH, DIRECTDEP, DIRECTDEBIT, REPEATPMT, OTHER)
    - Negative and positive TRNAMT; zero-cent TRNAMT on correction DELETE
    - CORRECTFITID + CORRECTACTION=REPLACE (corrected amount)
    - CORRECTFITID + CORRECTACTION=DELETE (removes a duplicate)
    - Full PAYEE aggregate (NAME, ADDR1, ADDR2, CITY, STATE, POSTALCODE, COUNTRY, PHONE)
    - ORIGCURRENCY aggregate (converted EUR→USD)
    - CURRENCY aggregate (unconverted foreign amount)
    - BANKACCTTO on a XFER transaction
    - CCACCTTO on a credit card payment transaction
    - REFNUM, CHECKNUM, SIC, EXTDNAME, PAYEEID
    - MEMO with XML-special characters (&amp; &lt; &gt;)
    - Datetime with full precision: YYYYMMDDHHMMSS.XXX[offset:TZ]
    - Datetime with date-only: YYYYMMDD (minimal valid form)
    - BANKTRANLISTP with HOLD pending transaction
    - Error STMTTRNRS (STATUS CODE 2003, no nested STMTRS)
    - BALLIST with BAL aggregate
    - Long FITID (up to 255 chars per spec, here 36-char UUID style)
    - CLTCOOKIE echoed back from request
